{"tid":637206,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實被炒！傳雲加獲賠900萬鎊","createTime":"2018-04-21T14:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T15:43:15.000Z","uid":1121,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b5587ac051f2c9b0b7d5858caf10dd64d04f82c4","tid":637206,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T14:47:47.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=NCDN%2BRr8j1hfn9LkkYcFGKEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=d9f42248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】英國傳媒指出，球季結束後離開阿仙奴實非雲加所願，其實是會方辭退他，而他將獲賠償900萬鎊。<br />\n<br />\n《每日郵報》報道，雲加（Arsene Wenger）於周五公開表示季後離開執教22年的阿仙奴，稱「是適當時間退下來」，但其實這並非他意願，那是董事局希望在下周歐霸盃4強上演前，決意向法國人開刀，從而增強凝聚力，令球迷不再糾纏狙擊雲加，更齊心支持「兵工廠」。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，眼見阿仙奴今季再次前4不保，本來支持雲加的高安基已對法國人失去耐性。由於雲加本來尚有1年合約，因此會方將為他賠償900萬鎊。<br />\n<br />\n前阿仙奴射手伊恩胡禮亦在《太陽報》撰文指，雲加並非那種未約滿就決定離開的人，故有理由相信他是被辭退，而非自願離開。"},{"pid":"8f416dbd798a5ea2b252f7e7dae4dc08f8355fea","tid":637206,"uid":1121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T14:47:59.000Z","msg":"要捉鬼！！！！"},{"pid":"7c0e4795c68d0062918b48a123f4e03508566364","tid":637206,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T14:50:27.000Z","msg":"錢對雲加真係完全唔重要"},{"pid":"d39d436bc3748b38def13541573ea0a352c776fa","tid":637206,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c0e4795c68d0062918b48a123f4e03508566364","tid":637206,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T14:50:27.000Z","msg":"錢對雲加真係完全唔重要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:10:23.000Z","msg":"呢句真"},{"pid":"41a1e368bc049b4368b79a8dcc4edc722b851706","tid":637206,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   挽留"},{"pid":"46a507efe69fc1c99471ac9be37c06c882be54d7","tid":637206,"uid":35930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:28:04